s: Summary: Four‑hour AI‑DeFi summit featuring keynotes, panel, workshop and networking for elite projects and VCs.
Topics: autonomous finance, AI‑driven liquidity, yield optimisation, on‑chain governance, token economics.
Speakers: AID founders, leading DeFi protocol CEOs, top‑tier venture capitalists.
r: Discover AI‑native financial primitives shaping next‑gen protocols.
Engage directly with capital allocators targeting AI‑DeFi synergies.
Participate in hands‑on workshops to prototype autonomous liquidity models.
